{"tid":1701494,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"極危險扮中立的人間記者會","createTime":"2019-11-09T05:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T23:54:09.000Z","uid":152455,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"908743e4da41bf9c15499064e43abe9d91333e3a","tid":1701494,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"我曾經比佢地d文厄左入去睇，用語斯文，用緊甜依毒藥洗人腦，我曾經去屌佢地係奶共網媒，但佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強調自己係中立，冇政治背景、冇顏色，仲話有咩誤會可以pm佢慢慢傾</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇政治背景會一味抹黑市威者？<br />\n<br />\n冇顏色會不停幫黑警洗白？<br />\n<br />\n唔係紅媒會幫人洗腦政府岩晒</span></strong></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日仲搵埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大波man</span></span></strong></span>做代言人，既然佢話有咩誤會慢慢傾，咁唔該咁多位入去慢慢同佢地d中立小編傾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下為其中一個危險洗腦文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#小薯家屬投稿<br />\n<br />\n繼續同兩位警嫂傾去．．<br />\n<br />\n我問: 你哋老公點睇香港變成咁，係咪覺得警察完全無錯先？<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 我覺得唔完美但可以接受（自嘲笑吓），每個機構嘅制度都有利有弊，可況前線執行嘅人要按當時嘅情況作出即時反應，談何容易，正如你之前所講，大家都面對緊前所未見嘅情況，每日變化都比計劃快，我相信警隊將來要會作出好多檢討同埋改善嘅措施，但呢一刻，前線人員日夜操勞，真係去個廁所都無時間啦⋯<br />\n<br />\n我：都係嘅，動亂未停，做事要有先後次序．．<br />\n<br />\n太太B 話: 講開又講，有啲好朋友諗住關心我地，就講：「其實你老公都係身不由己，佢都係聽上司話，打份工⋯」，啲朋友個個代入哂犯人心理，覺得警察係歹角！ 其實警員係有需要用適當的武力制服掙扎中的疑犯，或者根據經驗對方有可能會逃走，就要用武力！ 絕對唔係單單「聽上司話」⋯<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 朋友成日話，「識你哋兩公婆咁耐，知道你地哋為人，你哋唔係黑警」，叫我老公告發啲黑警出黎，還白警一個清白⋯又叫我老公諗下辭職唔做，搵返良知，真係黑人問號！<br />\n<br />\n我話: 其實，香港人普遍少留意國際新聞，以前香港示威好和平，所以冇見過用武力清場嘅場面，自然會覺得現時嘅警察濫用暴力啦。<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 最近大家都開始留意，其他國家係點樣處理呢啲示威活動，香港警察簡直係小巫見大巫！<br />\n<br />\n我: 咁又真係！出軍隊又有，幾日就開槍，有啲國家死人都有。<br />\n<br />\n太太B: 仲有，咁多年黎，香港治安真係好好，算係好和平，所以大家忘記咗警察係執法者，非法暴力示威者係犯人。有人想談公平，「公平」從來不等於「相同」，執法者需要比犯人有更多嘅權力先至可以有能力執法，保障市民嘅安全，唔通要警員赤手空拳咁執法先係公平？怎可能要求警察與犯人之間講「相同」？一個係疑犯，一個係執法人員，一個在明一個在暗！唔通人人都要配槍？人人都有催淚煙？咁樣先「公平」？<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 好似有個律師在電台話如果被警察攻擊，反抗係自衛！講到搶槍都係自衛咁，幾時警察執法變咗「互毆」？要對等？自衛？<br />\n<br />\n我搭嘴: 所以啲示威者而家都囤積武器⋯<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 啲人都合理化佢哋！警察有武器，「示威者都係用相對嘅武力去對抗咋嘛⋯」<br />\n<br />\n太太B: 其實邊到係相對？唔通警察又用氣油彈，漒水?⋯佢哋嘅「公平」係龍門任搬！警察鬧人「曱甴」當然係好唔禮貌啦，佢哋就大做文章話「去人性化」，「令人心寒」，「物化咗平民，所以好暴力！」咁當佢哋話「警蓄」，「狗仔狗女狗屋」，又得嫁喎！個「公平」突然唔見咗！<br />\n<br />\n太太A: 係喎！警察鬧人佢哋就話公開羞辱市民！啲勇武日鬧夜鬧:「黑警！你老婆比人x緊！」就無人表示覺得過份！<br />\n<br />\n我: 咁又真係例子多不勝數嘅⋯但著住制服講粗口，真係唔好！<br />\n<br />\n太太B: 咁梗係認同啦！但又咁講，幾時邊個講粗口都係唔好！難道警察被侮辱就要專業地忍受？不可以有情緒？示威者打藍絲就係「被挑釁」同情有可原，突然間又唔講公平了？講法變成「警察應有比市民更專業的忍耐力」。明顯地，警察被冠上各種不合理離地的「義務」，同時當要使用法例賦予佢地嘅「權力」去執法時，又比人話濫權，被要求要與犯法者平等，幾荒謬！<br />\n<br />\n太太B: 因為警察係well paid for it (人工包埋) 喎！ 呢幾個字難聽過粗口！人工包鏹水，割頸？包全家日夜被問候，仔女家人被欺凌？<br />\n<br />\n(vol 1 傳送門: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MMTXhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MMTXhQ&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=a65ec1cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MMTXhQ</a> )<br />\n(vol 2 傳送門: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NkrJtR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NkrJtR&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=e0678341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NkrJtR</a>)<br />\n(vol 3 傳送門: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oEb9gq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oEb9gq&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=8c009653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oEb9gq</a>)<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\n小編其實好認同，警察真係被妖魔化，傳媒，議員，大量社交專頁，大量假新聞，要嚮這個「亂世」保持清醒要出力！<br />\n<br />\n#人間記者會<br />\n#份糧咩都包<br />\n#亂世求清醒"},{"pid":"facf7f791b17244d1f7e6db073214d0dc0c9631c","tid":1701494,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v87L4Jh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv87L4Jh.jpg&h=8f20361f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bvE890.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bvE890.png&h=e4e56efd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pweiFgJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpweiFgJ.png&h=8d588355&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YH3SKJp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYH3SKJp.jpg&h=3830794c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7699978a9e5583ececf5ba3d5a26f1f87495bff","tid":1701494,"uid":200464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"冇見過黃絲話自己中立，<br />\n中立代表咩自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfbf49d655d6eab9f0c7770ff348ea86a635d69","tid":1701494,"uid":47659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"屌 個名都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b813880077812c436755ced2507dc035af317f75","tid":1701494,"uid":122976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"冷處理"},{"pid":"0f7f738030d4008d51294ace4ee6bda04f2552c8","tid":1701494,"uid":111425,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"見到大波man 已經fail 學咩人扮中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0739654104821ced07b059be5e6def313823fcf3","tid":1701494,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"全部人去report佢"},{"pid":"bbbe192cf7c311ae6b315447760fd27de483ddfa","tid":1701494,"uid":274329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"又抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c80893b7bcb18043d69ae5ed26b8ef9f0f3304","tid":1701494,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"幫正版助攻！其實係好事！"},{"pid":"c539baa647e9517362e57ff84bf28e14b181727d","tid":1701494,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDQ54Kn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDQ54Kn.jpg&h=401b6ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1760ef1d3c37d83e229f7991e1ebd4973dcc9a4f","tid":1701494,"uid":152455,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:26.000Z","msg":"做到黑警係受害人，狗仔媒撚慘呀<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGszX4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGszX4j.jpg&h=ab3cb4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSWth4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSWth4m.jpg&h=23425923&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHEuMXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHEuMXH.jpg&h=93d92bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AM182v6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAM182v6.jpg&h=c2913118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e6f65781e48417b86f17f6687dbaf0aa3aeca37","tid":1701494,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫佢推人氣做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者都嬲到走淨三間"},{"pid":"4232ffe1cc6aa04e15983010bfaae809de904f61","tid":1701494,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"最失敗應該係搵左咁有標誌性嘅大波man嚟扮中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個招牌淫邪笑容去拍牙膏廣告就岩"},{"pid":"885f53d4701001f02cf69519b73831cbed6921f5","tid":1701494,"uid":275692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"連出名中立嘅TVB都唔報就知唔洗理<br />\n都唔明樓豬緊張咩"},{"pid":"f923dee085908ae0bb8a11e69b83898301743872","tid":1701494,"uid":152455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"你屌9佢，佢就會用極理性口敏話自係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中立、講事實、歡迎pm佢討論</span></strong></span>，唔信你地可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ab710a9187142abdf00b03764fb3f60f91af6e","tid":1701494,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"你地唔講我完全唔知有呢咁嘅垃圾<br />\n唔好幫佢谷人氣啦屌"},{"pid":"b1d9d81cf887a4f7cfa67566c018f347929c321e","tid":1701494,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"陰間記者會。<br />\n藍屍十個十個劈頭第一句就係「我係中立既，我唔識咩係政治，只希望安份守紀打份工搵食」<br />\n垃撚圾！"},{"pid":"4b967f2ccb4d1a6cb29d807b825a11b517f4b42f","tid":1701494,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"咪撚幫佢煲熱啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff9d68bc0b33fa07f32bb84b5441f3f2cfea9c3","tid":1701494,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"屌拉返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ddf20dce6cbf8b3ce96e5d47f1cf767e1be96a","tid":1701494,"uid":58392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"report垃圾 page"},{"pid":"70a2db422c69bb70be03735d6c0c42755033f11e","tid":1701494,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲話中立同唔知大波man 係邊個既人都唔駛理佢地啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420b05dc7a40ddded281973062b4a0f51e19f400","tid":1701494,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,